| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2790 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 12ec1e80-74d1-5019-b961-1d3600a289bb"
